title: Gergő Ominger
text: Gergő Ominger (born 25 September 2002) is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Midfielder%20%28association%20football%29">midfielder</a> who plays for <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20II">Nemzeti Bajnokság II</a> club <a href="Cs%C3%A1kv%C3%A1ri%20TK">Csákvár</a>.
